"     <div class=\"reference\">",
"      Reproduced with permission from: Annane D, Bellissant E, Bollaert P, et al. Corticosteroids in the Treatment of Severe Sepsis and Septic Shock in Adults. JAMA 2009; 301:2362. Copyright &copy; 2009 American Medical Association. All rights reserved.",
"     </div>",
"    </br>",
